title: Shawn Messenger Fine Art Glass Cherry Blossoms Paperweight
description:
Signed by the artist, this magnificent paperweight captures a permanent moment of early spring.  White swirls represent the last bit of snow before spring explodes with the color and life of cherry blossoms.  Due to the handcrafted nature of this product size and color will vary slightly.  Made in the USA.  1.5 lbs.

3 1/4 in. sq.
